{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"58f45f158b","title":"转发华北军区高干会情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1780669195","index":0,"year":1950,"month":10,"day":28,"articleId":"58f45f158b"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"5e5b60d6c6","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"58f45f158b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"即中共华北军区委员会关于1950年10月20日至23日召开的华北军区高级干部会议情况的报告。报告中说，到会干部一致拥护中央和军委对朝鲜问题的决定。会议要求军队为适应新的形势，从各方面迅速地顺利地完成由和平到战争的转变，并确定了为实现这一转变采取的各项具体措施。会议讨论决定了以下几个问题：一、彻底克服和平麻思想；二、建立与改变组织机构，培养干部：三、加强战备：四、部队训练。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b30aa5a858","type":"title","text":"转发华北军区高干会情况报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"58f45f158b"},{"id":"5e5b60d6c6","type":"paragraph","text":"各大军区党委，并转所属二级军区党委及兵团级写军级党委局志们：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"58f45f158b"},{"id":"df9d217472","type":"paragraph","text":"我们认为华北军区党委会十月廿六日尚军委的报告则是正确的，这是按中央方针所作的具体计划和切实处置。请你们参照此文件，做出自己的具体计划和切实处置，并尽速报来，是为至要","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"58f45f158b"},{"id":"99f3f6bae1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"58f45f158b"},{"id":"3430cdef56","type":"paragraph","text":"十月廿八日于北京","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"58f45f158b"}],"page":{"id":"65d05a487e","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"58f45f158b","start":314,"end":314}}}},"__N_SSG":true}